videos.description: QB Sam Ehlinger runs the ball 16 yards for the first score of the game against the Oklahoma Sooners.
videos.headline: Texas strikes first against Oklahoma

videos.description: The Longhorns keep the Sooners out of the end zone with a goal-line stand in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Texas stops Oklahoma at the goal line

videos.description: QB Sam Ehlinger runs the ball 3 yards to put the Longhorns up 14-6 against the Sooners.
videos.headline: Texas QB punches in another TD

videos.description: Sam Ehlinger is taken down by Oklahoma's Amani Bledsoe on 3rd down, forcing the Longhorns to punt.
videos.headline: Oklahoma D sacks Texas QB

videos.description: Kyler Murray sends a 28-yard touchdown strike to CeeDee Lamb in the second quarter against the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Murray hits Lamb in end zone for TD

videos.description: Kyler Murray finds Grant Calcaterra on a 6-yard touchdown strike with the clock winding down on the first half against Texas.
videos.headline: Oklahoma scores before halftime

videos.description: Behind two touchdown passes from Kyler Murray, No. 5 Oklahoma carries a 20-14 lead over No. 14 Texas at halftime of the Big 12 Championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Oklahoma surges late to take lead over Texas at the half ) 2018/12/1 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Oklahoma surges late to take lead over Texas at the half

videos.description: Trey Sermon scores a 6-yard touchdown against the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Sermon scores easily for Sooners

videos.description: Oklahoma's defense takes down Sam Ehlinger for a loss of 7 yards.
videos.headline: Sooners sack Texas QB

videos.description: Collin Johnson hauls in Sam Ehlinger's 27-yard touchdown throw in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Ehlinger's TD pass cuts into Sooners' lead

videos.description: Sam Ehlinger finds Lil' Jordan Humphrey for a 5-yard touchdown to tie it with Oklahoma at 27 in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Ehlinger's TD pass ties it with Oklahoma

videos.description: Austin Seibert's 31-yard field goal bounces off of the upright, but converts to give the Sooners' lead.
videos.headline: Oklahoma takes lead by inches on lucky bounce

videos.description: Oklahoma's CeeDee Lamb turns the ball over to the Texas defense after a 56-yard reception.
videos.headline: Lamb fumbles it away after big gain

videos.description: Sam Ehlinger gets sacked in the end zone by Oklahoma's Tre Brown to push the lead to 5 in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Sooners blitz Ehlinger for safety

videos.description: Grant Calcaterra hauls in Kyler Murray's 18-yard touchdown pass with one hand.
videos.headline: Oklahoma scores on tremendous one-handed catch

videos.description: Lil' Jordan Humphrey's long touchdown gets called back after a holding penalty.
videos.headline: Penalty costs Texas kickoff return TD

videos.description: Oklahoma's Trey Norwood intercepts Sam Ehlinger's pass to give the ball back to the Sooners.
videos.headline: Norwood picks off Ehlinger to seal Big 12 title for Oklahoma

videos.description: Kyler Murray throws for 379 yards and 3 touchdowns as the Sooners get revenge vs. Texas and win the Big 12 title.

videos.headline: Kyler puts Big 12 championship 'at the top' of athletic career
